{"tid":1154350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【市場避險】資金避險撐起虛擬貨幣 比特幣曾突破8300美元","createTime":"2019-05-14T08:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T08:41:57.000Z","uid":252957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"551fba38fef67daabae8b12f4ed7d99e3b7416af","tid":1154350,"uid":252957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"受貿易戰連串負面消息影響，環球股市不穩，部分資金流入虛擬貨幣避險，推高比特幣價格。根據彭博數據，比特幣今日再創高位，一度升穿8300美元水平，高位見8331美元，日內最多漲5.94%，創近十個月高位。<br />\n<br />\n市場充斥不明朗因素，大量資金湧入虛擬貨幣，刺激比特幣愈升愈有。事實上，過去一個月，比特幣已累漲近60%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1557822903921&amp;issue=20190514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1557822903921%26issue%3D20190514&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=c41e2da1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1557822903921&amp;issue=20190514</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個要【避險】呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}